IN THE HIGH COURT OF PUNJAB & HARYANA, CHANDIGARH

CR No. 3650 of 1998 Date of decision: August 16, 2012 Vijay Kumar s/o Shri Fateh Chand Gosawami r/o Mohalla Kaistwarea, Narnaul, Tehsil Narnaul, Distt. Mohindergarh ....... Petitioner Versus Parbhu Dayal s/o Sh.Daddu Ram,r/o New Mandi, Narnaul Darvaja, Narnaul ........ Respondents CORAM: HON'BLE MR. JUSTICE K. KANNAN Present:- Mr. Jasbir Singh , Advocate for Mr. Sanjay Mittal, Advocate for the petitioner. None for the respondent. **** K. Kannan, J (oral). . Counsel for the petitioner states that the parties have entered into a compromise outside the Court and seeks for disposal of the case as such. . The Civil revision is dismissed as settled out of Court. (K. KANNAN) JUDGE August 16, 2012 archana
